## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/includes/deprecatedcontent-md.md)]  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="85687-103">Un <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> est le bloc de construction fondamental des workflows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-103">An <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> is the fundamental building block of workflows.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-104">Un <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> définit un ensemble de propriétés et d'événements, comme toutes les classes, mais également une logique d'exécution qui définit le comportement de l'activité au moment de l'exécution.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-104">An <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> defines a set of properties and events, such as any class, along with execution logic that defines the activity's run-time behavior.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-105">Un jeu de composants additionnels peut être associé à un <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-105">A set of additional components can be associated with an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-106">Ceux-ci incluent, mais ne sont pas limités à un validateur, un générateur de code, des sérialiseurs personnalisés et un concepteur.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-106">These include, but are not limited to a validator, a code generator, custom serializers, and a designer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="85687-107">Toutes les activités partagent un ensemble de propriétés défini sur la classe de base <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-107">All activities share a common set of properties defined on the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> base class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="85687-108">Chaque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> peut déclarer ses propres propriétés supplémentaires d'après ses besoins en étendant cette classe.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-108">Each <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> can declare its own additional properties according to its requirements by extending this class.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="85687-109">Les propriétés peuvent être définies comme propriétés CLR standard et comme propriétés de dépendance car <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> dérive de <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-109">Because <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> derives from <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject>, properties can be defined as standard CLR properties and as dependency properties.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="85687-110">La logique d'exécution d'un <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> répond à un contrat qui existe entre chaque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> et l'exécution du workflow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-110">The execution logic of an <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> fulfills a contract that exists between any <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> and the workflow runtime.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-111">Vous devez documenter la logique d'exécution de chaque <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> au sens fonctionnel, afin qu'un développeur de workflow qui utilise <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> sache comment il se comporte.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-111">You must document the execution logic of any <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> in a functional sense, so that a workflow developer who uses the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity> knows how it behaves.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-112">La logique d'exécution en elle-même est masquée du développeur de workflow qui inclut l'activité dans un workflow car elle fait partie d'un contrat qui existe uniquement entre l'exécution du workflow et <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-112">The execution logic itself is hidden from the workflow developer who includes the activity in a workflow, because the execution logic is part of a contract that exists strictly between the workflow runtime and the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="85687-113">Cet exemple définit une activité dont le but est d'envoyer un courrier électronique.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-113">This example defines an activity whose purpose is to send an email.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-114">L'activité définit une seule propriété, `Subject`, dont l'implémentation utilise une propriété de dépendance.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-114">The activity defines one property, `Subject`, that uses a dependency property in its implementation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-115">D'autres propriétés peuvent être définies de la même manière.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-115">Other properties can be defined in a similar way.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-116">La méthode `Execute` est substituée pour fournir la logique d'envoi d'un courrier électronique.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-116">The `Execute` method is overridden to provide the logic for sending the email.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="85687-117">Pour obtenir un exemple complet, consultez la [envoyer E-mail Activity, exemple](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/bfb5939e-60a9-4037-af4e-2cea9e654669).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="85687-117">For a complete example, see the [Send Email Activity Sample](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/bfb5939e-60a9-4037-af4e-2cea9e654669).</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public class SendEmail : Activity  
{  
    public static readonly DependencyProperty SubjectProperty =  
        DependencyProperty.Register("Subject", typeof(string), typeof(SendEmail));  
  
    public string Subject  
    {  
        get { return base.GetValue(SubjectProperty) as string; }  
        set { base.SetValue(SubjectProperty, value); }  
    }  
  
    // Define other properties...  
  
    protected override ActivityExecutionStatus Execute(ActivityExecutionContext executionContext)  
    {  
        // Logic to send the email goes here...  
        return ActivityExecutionStatus.Closed;  
    }  
}  
```

